input#mainCat(type="hidden", value=locals.mainCat)
.panelmargin.small-12.medium-12.large-9.columns
  dl.accordion(data-accordion='data-accordion')
    dd.nopadding.active
      a(href='#arrangers')
        .small-12.columns.filterpanel.borderbottom
          .filterpanel.small-8.medium-8.large-4.columns
            h2 Arrangörer
          .filterpanel.small-4.medium-4.large-8.columns.text-right
            p.show-for-large-up
              | Här hittar du arrangörer som är proffs på att organisera, inspirera och administrera. Du filtrerar listan genom att välja en eller flera kategorier.
            p.hide-for-large-up
              | Dölj/Visa
              br
              | filtrering
      #arrangers.content
        .small-12.columns.filterpanel
          .filterpanel.small-12.medium-12.large-4.columns
            ul.filtering
              - var res = 0;
              - for (i=0 ; i<(locals.cats.length/3); i++) {
                - var item = locals.cats[i];
                - res = i+1;
                li
                  input(id="#{item._id}", type='checkbox')
                  label(for='#{item._id}') #{item.displayName}
              - }
              
              span.hide-for-large-up
                - for (i=res; i<locals.cats.length; i++) {
                  - var item = locals.cats[i];
                  li
                    input(id="#{item._id}", type='checkbox')
                    label(for='#{item._id}') #{item.displayName}
                - }
          .large-4.columns.show-for-large-up
            ul.filtering
              - for (i=res ; i<(locals.cats.length*.66667); i++) {
                - var item = locals.cats[i];
                - res = i+1;
                li
                  input(id="#{item._id}", type='checkbox')
                  label(for='#{item._id}') #{item.displayName}
              - }
          .large-4.columns.show-for-large-up
            ul.filtering
              - for (i=res ; i<(locals.cats.length); i++) {
                - var item = locals.cats[i];
                - res = i+1;
                li
                  input(id="#{item._id}", type='checkbox')
                  label(for='#{item._id}') #{item.displayName}
              - }
    dl